cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.DL 

The paper focuses on the extraction of structured information from Wikipedia articles, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of infoboxes and the extraction of historical events also involve database technologies (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of machine learning techniques for event extraction, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.DL).
